channel.title: Wanna make a walking cript but totally new to java and aryan
channel.description: Well, I am really new to java and aryan. I have never scripted before for aryan , but did small edits for sbot2 (if that matters). I am wanting to make a walking script. If anyone can help get me started or give me a skeleton of one I would really appreciate it. Ive been looking at other walking scripts and they either 1 dont work or 2 the codes is extremly messy. If anyone can help I would really appreciate it. Hopefully I will stop leeching all my scripts and maybe start making some good ones :)
